<template>
    <el-table :data="tableData">
        <el-table-column prop="id" label="ID" width="60">

        <el-table-column prop="roleId" label="地址">
        </el-table-column>
    </el-table>
</template>

<style scoped>

</style>

<script>
    export default {
      name: "Main",
      data() {
        return {
          tableData: []
        }
      },
      methods:{
        loadGet(){
          this.$axios.get(this.$httpUrl+'/user/list').then(res=>res.data).then(res=>{
              console.log(res)
          })
        },
        loadPost(){
          this.$axios.post(this.$httpUrl+'/user/listP',{}).then(res=>res.data).then(res=>{
              console.log(res)
              this.tableData=res
          })
        }
      },
      beforeMount(){
          //this.loadGet();
          this.loadPost()
      }
    }
</script>
